 ABOUT PYFIX

PyFix is a script for the Greasemonkey (http://www.greasespot.net/)
which extends or just fixes pytal.de. 
PyFix will only be interesting for you if you are signed up there.

 FEATURES

Currently, PyFix provides a wide range of features. If you have any idea,
do not hesitate to contact me.

 * Add Accesskey to submit post form
 * Add some Tabs to header
 * Advanced editor for posts
   * Changes Syntax of URL-BBCode
     Before: [url="Example"]http://example.com[/url]
     After:  [url="http://example.com"]Example[/url]
   * Insert smileys at postition of cursor
   * New smileys
   * Upload pictures to image.gd while posting
   * Have a look at the thread you are posting to while posting
 * Confirm deleting/closing of postings
 * Append a signature to every posting
 * Highlight your own nick
 * Force usage of encrypted connections
 
